21
00:03:44,070 --> 00:03:45,190
Or to never tell her that

22
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:47,390
you met someone you shouldn't have met?

23
00:03:50,790 --> 00:03:52,390
All of them.

24
00:03:53,390 --> 00:03:54,470
If you don't tell my sister,

25
00:03:54,470 --> 00:03:55,800
all of us will be safe.

26
00:03:56,510 --> 00:03:57,840
If you tell my sister...

27
00:03:59,150 --> 00:04:00,550
all of us are doomed.

28
00:04:20,899 --> 00:04:23,540
Are you crazy? Can you use your brain?

29
00:04:24,710 --> 00:04:25,670
If Guan Xue dies,

30
00:04:25,670 --> 00:04:27,730
everything I've done will be in vain.

31
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,560
What's wrong with killing a spy?

32
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:33,750
What's wrong with killing a Japanese?

33
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:34,750
I'm your brother!

34
