36
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:56,990
Did you call my house?

37
00:04:57,110 --> 00:04:59,230
I called 10 minutes ago, but no one answered.

38
00:04:59,230 --> 00:05:00,630
I don't think Kai's home.

39
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:35,990
Give me a drink.

40
00:05:38,230 --> 00:05:40,870
I've been learning about Japanese wine recently.

41
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:42,990
The water in the Hyogo is hard.

42
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:45,230
The wine made from it

43
