48
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:55,790
The last time I was attacked...

49
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:56,450
And smooth.

50
00:05:57,550 --> 00:05:59,070
Was many years ago.

51
00:05:59,990 --> 00:06:01,670
You were on a business trip.

52
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:05,420
