55
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:16,600
You were severely punished too.

56
00:06:25,350 --> 00:06:26,550
Which one do you want?

57
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:31,870
I have a hunch the person who tried to kill me was Manchukuo's Robin Hood.

58
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:44,990
Did you find him?

59
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:46,550
Not yet.

60
00:06:47,030 --> 00:06:49,110
But someone saw a truck parked at the intersection.

61
00:06:49,110 --> 00:06:51,640
We are basically sure that it's a sniper spot.

62
00:06:53,110 --> 00:06:54,830
The sniper spot is on a truck.

63
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:56,470
A scrapped truck.

64
00:06:58,150 --> 00:06:59,880
There was no trace at the scene.

65
00:07:01,350 --> 00:07:02,070
They found the bullet hole

66
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:03,470
but the ballistics is high.

67
00:07:03,470 --> 00:07:04,600
What does that mean?

68
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,460
That they're not skilled?

69
00:07:15,230 --> 00:07:17,430
The driver Xiaochuan was shot to death.

70
00:07:18,590 --> 00:07:20,870
I’m going to your home to pick Kai up.

71
