76
00:08:22,690 --> 00:08:25,150
If there are any still alive, just kill them.

77
00:08:25,590 --> 00:08:26,270
Yes!

78
00:08:30,690 --> 00:08:32,650
Check over there.

79
00:09:06,670 --> 00:09:08,070
