80
00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:09,310
Not yet.

81
00:09:09,310 --> 00:09:10,070
Go.

82
00:09:43,740 --> 00:09:44,580
Zhuowen.

83
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:50,630
Zhuowen!

84
00:09:51,990 --> 00:09:52,830
Zhuowen!

85
00:09:53,710 --> 00:09:54,620
Here's one!

86
00:10:03,100 --> 00:10:04,630
