91
00:10:20,190 --> 00:10:21,030
Let him go!

92
00:10:23,630 --> 00:10:24,310
Let go!

93
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:56,550
Brother, Brother!

94
00:10:57,310 --> 00:10:57,950
Brother!

95
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:39,590
Miss.

96
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:42,550
Miss!

97
00:12:05,410 --> 00:12:07,380
Please save my brother.

98
00:12:10,590 --> 00:12:11,230
Let's go.

99
00:12:55,430 --> 00:12:56,070
Salute!

100
00:13:05,070 --> 00:13:06,390
Too formal.

101
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:07,470
At ease.

102
00:13:07,950 --> 00:13:08,590
Harada.

103
00:13:08,990 --> 00:13:09,590
Yes.

104
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:11,760
Didn't you make it clear to them?

105
00:13:12,830 --> 00:13:13,900
Sorry, it slipped my mind.

106
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,500
You should have informed me.

107
00:13:16,590 --> 00:13:17,450
Section Chief.

108
00:13:19,390 --> 00:13:20,270
It's because

109
00:13:20,450 --> 00:13:23,250
I heard that Section Chief Guan Xue

110
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,330
came over on the way last night.

111
00:13:26,350 --> 00:13:28,750
Thank you for your concern, Section Chief.

112
00:13:32,430 --> 00:13:33,990
On the surface,

113
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:39,190
